description: With the record of 1-1, CJ needs this match to be on top. He is getting the hang of NK and he's becoming quite a brute. Matthew Singer is a tough boy from Southern California. He's new to NK but he has combat training in the military. Matthew visited the site and begs to be on NK. This is his chance to kick some ass. For this match, the loser has to give up his hole to the winner and be his bitch for the day.
title: CJ vs Matthew Singer
